{
  "title": "Incredibly Citrusy Malaysian Asparagus Stir Fry",
  "description": "A flexitarian friendly Malaysian dish featuring asparagus, with a burst of citrus flavor and wok hei, served in a donabe vessel, perfect for a solo dinner",
  "cuisine": "Malaysian",
